Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.29,0:01:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.98,0:01:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's his daily routine, but does Father \Nreally have to do that every morning?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.45,0:01:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And wow, that was a pretty racy dream... {ecchi}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.70,0:01:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming, Mother!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.28,0:01:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish he thought about his daughter’s \Nwell-being once in a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.07,0:01:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That “HYAA!” scream of his \Nis going to throw off my whole biological cycle.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.71,0:01:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.54,0:01:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear... \NDo I seriously need to go up a size again?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.05,0:01:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Growing up is such a pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! A matchmaking meeting? {episode title}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.24,0:01:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.11,0:01:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm only sixteen!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.91,0:01:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the Hagiwara family tradition.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.23,0:02:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are to begin marriage meetings at age sixteen.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.22,0:02:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.86,0:02:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, Mother!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.40,0:02:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father picked out this kimono for you. {I assume it's about kimono}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.68,0:02:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so elegant and lovely—\Nperfect for just such an occasion!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.17,0:02:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage meetings\Nare a woman’s training for life.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.40,0:02:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re lucky. The candidate is the nephew of Master Hori, ninth-dan of the Kendo Federation,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.56,0:02:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,a respectable young man who'll eventually inherit his family’s trade company.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.04,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.94,0:02:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s more than suitable for you! {lit: he has no shortcomings}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.83,0:02:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mother...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a first time for everything, Saori.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.84,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay! Have a good day.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! He never even asked me!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone needs to go wake up Yuji-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, do it for once, will you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.32,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do {\i1}I{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}have to wake \Nthe horror-movie-addicted freeloader? {isourou - someone who was foisted on them and lives with them for free}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.36,0:02:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t say that. A woman should know \Nhow to make a man rise. {double entendre - make both a man stand upright and make his dick stand up}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.17,0:02:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, Mother... Are you saying \Nyou do that for Yuji every morning? {helping him get an erection or something}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.21,0:03:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course I could never do \Nsomething so shameless!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.58,0:03:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I was just joking.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.67,0:03:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{But you're also so stiff, trying to be Yamato Nadeshiko in every way you can.} You should lighten up, instead of always being a boring, perfect housewife.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.15,0:03:19.04,Thought,,0,0,0,,And Yuji is already too spoiled anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.04,0:03:23.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,{“Breakfast room service” in this house? \NFather's incorrigible!} {father is father - probably means he insisted that all men in the house should receive that} On top of that, insisting that he gets room service—Father's incorrigible!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.90,0:03:27.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,Okay, sure, he took in the son \Nof his best friend from kendo club...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,But he’s coddling him way too much!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.92,0:03:32.26,Thought,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know what hardship is.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.26,0:03:36.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,Dad has no idea he spends his days laying about!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! How long are you gonna sleep?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I get it, I'm getting up, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.44,0:03:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, snap! My morning wood is here! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it there for me, would you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re just saying that \Nso you can fall back asleep, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Don't step into my sacred domain!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster Bash! {????? monsuta *** }
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! My film!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.97,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Close call...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn’t I?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.68,0:04:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.81,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Not there again! {?????? oreta?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I... can't... {???? probably just some sounds of shock}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.06,0:04:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, okay? \NDon’t be mad, Saori! Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, idiot, idiot! \NI don’t even want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You tasteless, perverted AIDS carrier! {???? eizu? she's calling him aids? }
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.65,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn’t that a little harsh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.84,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I’m sorry for scaring you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you’re the one who ruined my masterpiece!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that a masterpiece?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was disgusting!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.47,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! It’s supposed to be disgusting! \NIt’s an SFX horror mask!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{Just stop clinging to me already!} I don't care, just stop being so clingy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's clingy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.45,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We go to the same school, so we have \Nto take the same route, that's all there is to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.62,0:05:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, that there is Hagiwara Saori. {waka here is probably waka-sama - young master}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.03,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's even cuter in person. {beauty}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.61,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As befits the pride and only daughter of Hagiwara Yusaku, principal of Jouka Academy. {maybe that school name is a joke in itself}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.53,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, handling some fresh prey \Nonce in a while might be entertaining. {fuck me this show has got its own harako tsutomu}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it! Some man you are! {??? could be "despite being a man", could be "you stink of a man"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! Some woman you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.89,0:05:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san! Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Yuki. {??? yukitte? some special name for her or just saori's idiosyncrasy?}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.59,0:05:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not with Manami today?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.11,0:05:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s the thing...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.92,0:06:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami might be coming straight from an overnight stay today.  {meaning she stayed somewhere else and didn't come home and will come to school from that other place}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez! Another new boyfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.13,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She called this morning and said, \N“Go on ahead without me.”
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.64,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She had that bittersweet voice, \Nlike the one right after you do {\i1}that{\i0}. {have sex}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You do {\i1}what{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.78,0:06:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Don’t make me say it out loud.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.51,0:06:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Manami’s on another level of maturity compared to us, so it’s not surprising.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do again?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.63,0:06:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.83,0:06:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no... What do I say?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.79,0:06:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, stop talking about others \Nlike they're some man-huntresses. {wantonness; man-crazy}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry! \NI was kinda jealous, so it just happened...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.55,0:06:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t be silly. \NYou just have an overactive imagination.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, my parents suddenly dumped a matchmaking meeting on me this morning. {omiai}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.45,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m totally at a loss.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.18,0:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Sounds lovely.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.78,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way! It sounds suffocating. \NAnd I'm only in my second year of high school!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? \NWhat if he turns out to be a hot guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.44,0:07:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he’s good in bed, \Nthat’s a win, right? {technician}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Now hold up, Manami!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.09,0:07:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going there in a kimono? Then you must go fully traditional and not wear any underwear. {furisode - long-sleeved kimono; jun nihonshiki - purely japanese ceremony}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Be serious!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, today must be cursed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re lucky, you know that, Saori?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.19,0:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The second we step onto campus, \Nboys and girls are completely segregated.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re not even allowed \Nto see each other inside the building.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.57,0:07:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s practically a prison!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.41,0:07:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,True!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.62,0:07:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re literally the unluckiest high school girls in modern Japan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.52,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That sucks... So if Saori gets a chance to actually meet a guy, she should count herself lucky.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s complicated...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.67,0:07:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we’re shooting the climax scene. \NNo screw-ups, got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.93,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it won't be as impactful without a real girl \Nplaying the heroine in distress. {being chased}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can’t you do something about that, Sakazaki?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.98,0:07:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could, do you think I’d have Asai do the cross-dressing? Right, Teruo?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A-About that...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.36,0:08:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... I want to drop out of this role.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.23,0:08:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well... something came up.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teruo! \NYou can’t do that to us now!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.06,0:08:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no other girl who could play it—\Nwe're totally out of options!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.69,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}I object.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.23,0:08:19.73,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}I know Jouka Academy is prestigious \Nand famous for its enforcement of rules,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.70,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}but resorting to a suspension?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.75,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Especially for something \Nthat happened off campus after school...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.75,0:08:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn’t Edo or Meiji Japan, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.49,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh... I agree with Akimoto-sensei completely.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How sweet of you, Fukuike-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.15,0:08:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn’t this the perfect time \Nto reconsider our school rules?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.96,0:08:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Modernizing the school is a matter of utmost urgency for the proper guidance of our students.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuike-sensei,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.43,0:08:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,remember your position.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.31,0:08:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Akimoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget the students \Nwho caused the scandal—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.93,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yamada Miharu of Class 2-C,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and Asai Teruo of Class 2-G—{\i0} {we saw the boys' class was 2-C but it's actually supposed to be the girls' class, in manga the boys are in 2-G}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.95,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,are from your respective homerooms!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is exactly why we want to help them!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Fukuike-sensei?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.89,0:09:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.04,0:09:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.58,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Director, please look closely at this photographic evidence again.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.99,0:09:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem isn’t that they \Ngot caught on photo, but rather,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.65,0:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}where{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}it was taken: \Nin front of a disreputable hotel!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.28,0:09:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Principal, do they appear to be entering it? \NOr rather, going away from it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.41,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put it that way, \NI suppose they most likely are leaving, yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, guilty until proven innocent! {utagawashiki wa bassezu - means "innocent until proven guilty; suspicion alone is not grounds for punishment; in dubio pro reo​" but I think he changed the ending to bassuru - reverting the meaning, because he was advocating for punishment before, though it's hard to tell }
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That has been the rule of our academy
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,since its founding under \NLord Hagiwara Shinnosuke, Director!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.57,0:10:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the verdict: until the facts are clear, both will be suspended for an indefinite period of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! That's so harsh!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.78,0:10:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.73,0:10:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Asai's been busy!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Teruo...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.13,0:10:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Now my dad’s gonna get the notice.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.15,0:10:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no way he’ll let me out \Nto go on location shoots.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.91,0:10:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our masterpiece—\N{\i1}Intestine Alien: Dancing on Friday the 13th{\i0}?! {lit: cursed friday}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Awful! This is so awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Miharu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.66,0:10:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a completely pure relationship! \NIt’s true! Believe me!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it {\i1}had{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}happened, \Nyou shouldn’t be ashamed. {meaning even if you did go to a love hotel}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{With love, that’s a natural course of things.} When you're in love, that's totally natural.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.64,0:10:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I simply {\i1}love{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}when Manami-san says something mature like that! {yuki is herself, the green hair, manami is red hair}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ya agree? \NAin't that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.69,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The real villain is the backward \N customs of this outdated school!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.17,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{If it comes to this, I should go to my father... \NNo, to the Director!} {Removed the 'maybe' because it was a three liner otherwise} If it comes down to it, I'll go to my father... \N No, to the Director!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.44,0:10:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And use my own body to show him just how immoral schoolgirls can be. How about it? {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san, are you serious?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.22,0:11:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'll also make sure to humiliate him \Nat that damned matchmaking meeting. {current/this time's}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you can pull that off?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.81,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of your sensitive mother—\Nshe'd probably faint, or die, even.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.90,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When you put it that way...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not happening.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Miharu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.24,0:11:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we work together, \Nmaybe we can push through this crisis!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.88,0:11:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No good after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.21,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! A heroine in distress has to be \N a pretty girl, end of discussion!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.94,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In horror, it’s crucial that the difference between you and the grotesque alien be striking! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.00,0:11:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But your looks will make the audience puke their guts out—no laughs, no sympathy, no nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.14,0:11:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to try it at least once...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.81,0:11:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no choice! \NYou know someone has to stand in for Asai. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.82,0:11:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{Am I getting forced \Ninto a matchmaking meeting, after all?} Am I really going to be forced to \N attend the matchmaking meeting?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.49,0:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.64,0:11:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, Yuji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Now you're getting it, Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It was an accident! I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.81,0:12:05.45,Overlap,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about I forgive you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.02,0:12:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But in exchange, be the heroine in my movie! \NI’ve been asking forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.55,0:12:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.27,0:12:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I’d rather go to that awful matchmaking meeting\Nthan play a character in your creepy movie!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, matchmaking meeting!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.11,0:12:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Matchmaking...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Your father just called.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What about how {\i1}I{\i0}{\i0\fsp8} {\fsp0}feel?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.97,0:12:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was supposed to be this Sunday!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.06,0:12:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But the boy you were supposed to be meeting \Nhas sudden plans to fly to New York tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not my problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.23,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he saw your photo, \Nhe insisted on meeting you before he leaves.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he’s utterly smitten with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Father is simply hopeless.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.35,0:13:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He sounds like a servant \Ncarrying out his lord’s orders.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.75,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems your old kendo teacher, \NMaster Hori, personally begged him, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.62,0:13:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your poor father panicked himself half to death. So please, just go. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.75,0:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez... You know I can't refuse you anything, Mother. {lit: I'm weak to mother}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.55,0:13:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.83,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let them drag me around like this, \Nwho knows what they'll come up with next?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up, Manami... you’re the only one \NI can rely on right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki? Thank god you’re there, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.74,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuki, my matchmaking meeting is tonight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.34,0:14:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Congratulations! \NSo you made up your mind?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.78,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Yuki! That’s not it. \NI’m terrified of how this is unfolding!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.61,0:14:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I’m losing control without even realizing it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.90,0:14:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I also can't reach Manami \Nat such a crucial time. {???? lit: such a thing happened to manami - but we haven't seen anything happening to her, so either they forgot to film it or she means something like "what would manami have done in a situation like this?"}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.65,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san, are you shaking?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my maiden’s intuition.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.13,0:14:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like something dirty is waiting for me there. I'm so scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.48,0:14:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! I’ll track down Manami-san for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.03,0:14:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely something only she can handle.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I need her! {????? idk memototte}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The venue?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,She's late!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.10,0:14:58.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,What if she's unable to reach Manami?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,There’s no one else who could pull me out of this mess.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,That’s it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.64,0:15:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Manami! Perfect timing. \NA call from Yuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it’s me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori is?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... and?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The heir to the Hori Company? {literally harako lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! His name’s Hideki, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I’m on my way.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.67,0:15:35.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,That bastard! He still hasn't had enough?! {????? **** mada}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you’re doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my harem.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.18,0:15:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hideki...!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.06,0:15:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A little ritual. Anyone who becomes my servant \Nhas to enjoy this game.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.90,0:16:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.70,0:16:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! Is this the\N“world-class party” you bragged about?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.41,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right, Manami.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.26,0:16:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I’d teach you \Nhow the upper crust has its fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You disgust me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.68,0:16:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Money? Jewels?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.51,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Become my slave and I’ll give you anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.58,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.73,0:16:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.44,0:16:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, our Hideki-kun has got a grand future. \N{I think he fears nothing in this world!} He doesn't know the meaning of the word "fear"!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.04,0:16:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.43,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If he’d just master the Old Master's kendo, \Nthen he’d really be invincible.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.27,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But that part is hopeless, it seems... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.59,0:17:05.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,The closer I look, the prettier she gets.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,I’m turning twenty-eight next year.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.42,0:17:11.38,Thought,,0,0,0,,With a girl like this, \NI might even consider a real engagement.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.06,0:17:15.09,Thought,,0,0,0,,But first, I should sample the goods.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,Is Yuji-kun even coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.66,0:17:22.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,But it looks like this might actually end normally. \NGuess I panicked for nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.06,0:17:25.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,Maybe my intuition isn’t that great after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.01,0:17:31.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh gosh, why did I jump up like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.05,Thought,,0,0,0,,Did it kick in?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon! A beast dressed as high society! {?????? nc what's first word, oni da?}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.97,0:17:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong? Feeling faint?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.06,0:17:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You should lie down a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.52,0:18:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re a curious one, aren’t you? {idk why}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.93,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Following me this far \Nwasn’t just the drugs talking.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping the kimono on \Nmakes it even hotter. {furisode}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.76,0:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll take you to even nicer parties someday.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.51,0:18:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, spread your legs for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.81,0:18:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.28,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.74,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You’re a guy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You bargain-bin playboy. {false; pseudo-; quasi-; would-be; sham; pretended; mock​}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.41,0:19:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Always judging by appearances, never seeing what’s real.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way a guy like you
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.00,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,could ever see through my makeup!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.35,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m the special-effects makeup genius\Nfrom Jouka Academy—Sakazaki Yuji! {??? **** jouka gakuin}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn that into your brain!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.85,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.16,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.44,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hori Hideki!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m so glad you came!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.42,0:19:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... N-No! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami, stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{??? banzai?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.42,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready... Action!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Cut! Cut!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My clothes got snagged on the bush.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.74,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Moron! Clutz! Do it properly!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? \NWhat makes you think you're any better? {????? sonna ni **** yo; maybe "don't yell that kind of thing"}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.83,0:20:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Brute! Pervert! Knucklehead! {?????? only got hentai}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Comment: 10,0:22:22.73,0:22:25.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 6,0:20:30.23,0:20:34.78,Song,,0,0,0,,{BECAUSE by ScooP; got full lyrics from EB's booklet: 見ようともしなかったことに\N君は今瞳を向け始めてる\N「ゴメンネ」とうつむいた君\N僕にはもう信じさせるものがない\N崩れそうなその肩を二度と\N僕は抱けない\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 離れて行く\N怖いなんて言葉にはつばを吐いてきた\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 小さくなる\Nあの頃は君の好きなもの すべて好きだったのに\N手に届く限りのもので\N君は今 幸せを創りあげたね\N夢を側に置きたい君\N夢だけはまだ追い続けていたい僕\N君はたぶん僕以外の男に\N抱かれるんだね\N君が思ってるより 僕は強くないさ\N誰も君の代わりできないから\NBecause I miss you, Baby. 振り向かない\N君の笑顔 今僕の瞳駆けめぐる\NBecause I miss you, Baby. もう見えない\N届かない僕の愛も夢もこの声さえも\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\N小さくなる\NBecause I miss you, Baby.\Nもう見えない} You're starting to turn your eyes
Dialogue: 6,0:20:35.84,0:20:44.50,Song,,0,0,0,,to something you never even tried to see
Dialogue: 6,0:20:45.56,0:20:50.32,Song,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry," you said, bowing your head
Dialogue: 6,0:20:51.15,0:21:00.22,Song,,0,0,0,,And I no longer had anything you could believe in
Dialogue: 6,0:21:01.28,0:21:15.43,Song,,0,0,0,,I can never hold those shaking shoulders again {crumbling}
Dialogue: 6,0:21:15.43,0:21:18.95,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, Baby
Dialogue: 6,0:21:18.95,0:21:22.29,Song,,0,0,0,,I won't look back
Dialogue: 6,0:21:22.29,0:21:30.67,Song,,0,0,0,,Your smile is flashing through my eyes now
Dialogue: 6,0:21:30.67,0:21:33.70,Song,,0,0,0,,Because I miss you, Baby
Dialogue: 6,0:21:34.20,0:21:37.66,Song,,0,0,0,,I can't see you anymore
Dialogue: 6,0:21:37.66,0:21:49.48,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, my dreams, and even my voice won't reach you
Dialogue: 6,0:21:45.85,0:21:49.48,Song,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H880049&}Because I miss you, baby
